page.title: 02Nicola Sullivan
page.content: I got up at 7.55am and went into the bathroom to have a wash.I came out at 8.10am and got dressed.Then I went downstairs at 8.15am after making my bed and tidying my room.I had my breakfast and fed my fish and went back upstairs at 8.30am. I brushed my hair and cleaned my teeth.Then I put my school things in my bag and said goodbye to my mum, dad and my baby brother and left the house at 8.45am and went to school.At 9.00am we came in and did our work until 10.40am and had playtime.After play we worked until 12.00 to have lunch.We had silent reading and worked until 3.00. I walked home and played until 6.00pm then had my tea.I did the washing up and watched T.V.Then I got ready for bed and went to bed at 8.30.
